    "A novel approach is employed, dissecting the generated text into elemental facts and computing scores for the factual components endorsed by the knowledge source.",
    "• FactualityPrompt (Lee et al, 2022).",
    "The FactualityPrompt dataset evaluates the factual accuracy of textual outputs generated by LLMs.",
    "With a dataset size of 16K English samples, evenly split into 8K authentic prompts and 8K fabricated prompts, it is an adaptation derived from the FEVER dataset.",
    "The study delves into the influence of two types of prompts on the factual accuracy of LLMs, replicating real-world situations with input inaccuracies."
